`1 + tâ‚پ.size + tâ‚‚.size < 1 + (2 ^ tâ‚‚.height) + (2 ^ tâ‚‚.height)`
`1 + tâ‚پ.size + tâ‚‚.size < 1 + 2 * (2 ^ tâ‚‚.height)`
`1 + tâ‚پ.size + tâ‚‚.size < 2 * (2 ^ tâ‚‚.height)`
which is exactly what we need.

